PN,43401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778076676
OL,3,CWoman and ex-partner killed in Bristol
OL,4,Cexplosion named by police
OL,6,FTwo people killed by an explosion at a
OL,7,Fhouse in Bristol have been named as 35-
OL,8,Fyear-old Jo Shaw and her 41-year-old
OL,9,Fformer partner Ryan Kelly.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,12,Fdomestic incident on Sterncourt Road,
OL,13,FFrenchay, at 6:17am on Sunday 3 May.
OL,15,FThe call was from a person inside the
OL,16,Fproperty - where Jo lived - who stated
OL,17,Fa man that they knew had forced entry
OL,18,Fto the house.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778076676
OL,3,CWoman and ex-partner killed in Bristol
OL,4,Cexplosion named by police
OL,6,FSeveral police units were dispatched
OL,7,Fto the address while the caller stayed
OL,8,Fon the line. Before police arrived, an
OL,9,Fexplosion occurred which killed the
OL,10,Fpair and injured a further three
OL,11,Fpeople, including a child.
OL,13,FThese three people, including the
OL,14,Fperson who called police, were treated
OL,15,Ffor minor injuries and did not need to
OL,16,Fstay in hospital.
OL,18,FThe first officers arrived at the
OL,19,Fproperty at 6.34am and were joined by
OL,20,Fthe fire and ambulance services
OL,21,Fshortly afterwards.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778076676
OL,3,CWoman and ex-partner killed in Bristol
OL,4,Cexplosion named by police
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said they
OL,7,Fhave officially recorded Jo's death as
OL,8,Fa homicide.
OL,10,FThey added that they will refer
OL,11,Fthemselves to the Independent Office
OL,12,Ffor Police Conduct because the deaths
OL,13,Foccurred following prior police
OL,14,Fcontact, specifically other domestic
OL,15,Fincidents prior to Sunday.
OL,17,F"We know people will be shocked and
OL,18,Fupset to learn of the horrendous
OL,19,Fevents that happened on Sunday
OL,20,Fmorning," said Superintendent Matt
OL,21,FEbbs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778076676
OL,3,CWoman and ex-partner killed in Bristol
OL,4,Cexplosion named by police
OL,6,F"We know everyone's thoughts and
OL,7,Fsympathies will be with (Jo's)
OL,8,Fdevastated family. Specially-trained
OL,9,Fofficers are providing them with
OL,10,Fupdates and support.
OL,12,F"We recognise there is significant
OL,13,Finterest in what happened, but at the
OL,14,Fcentre of it there are many people
OL,15,Fgrieving and we would please ask
OL,16,Feveryone respects that and gives them
OL,17,Fthe privacy they want."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@YpmoD@^pntD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778076676
OL,3,CWoman and ex-partner killed in Bristol
OL,4,Cexplosion named by police
OL,6,FSupt Ebbs added: "Police activity
OL,7,Fcontinues to be carried out at the
OL,8,Fproperty in Sterncourt Road and we
OL,9,Fexpect this will take several days to
OL,10,Fbe completed.
OL,12,F"We would like to reassure the public
OL,13,Fthere is not believed to be any wider
OL,14,Frisk to safety and this is not being
OL,15,Ftreated as terrorism-related.
OL,17,F"As previously stated, we believe the
OL,18,Fcause of the explosion to be
OL,19,Fdeliberate. Analysis work of the
OL,20,Fexplosive device has not yet been
OL,21,Fcompleted.
OL,26,@nD@ROUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778076676
OL,3,CWoman and ex-partner killed in Bristol
OL,4,Cexplosion named by police
OL,6,F"We will share all details of our
OL,7,Fenquiries with the coroner so they can
OL,8,Fmake a final determination around how
OL,9,Fthe deaths occurred in due course.
OL,11,F"Officers remain in the area and
OL,12,Fpeople can speak to them if they have
OL,13,Fconcerns they wish to discuss with us.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778076676
OL,3,CWoman and ex-partner killed in Bristol
OL,4,Cexplosion named by police
OL,6,F"Finally, we would like to reiterate
OL,7,Four thanks to emergency services,
OL,8,Fother agencies and volunteers for
OL,9,Ftheir support over the weekend. This
OL,10,Fremains a challenging and complex
OL,11,Fenquiry, and we are ensuring our
OL,12,Fofficers and staff have access to any
OL,13,Fsupport they need."
OL,15,FPeople living in neighbouring houses
OL,16,Fwho were evacuated after the explosion
OL,17,Fwere told to return home on Monday 4
OL,18,FMay.
OL,20,FA police presence remains on
OL,21,FSterncourt Road.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
